attributes.Long form description: The instructor asks the student to turn on the Nintendo. The student presses the black button on the top of the console and waits for the console to boot up properly.  Then the instructor asks the student to turn off the console. The instructor first instructs the student to hold down the top button of the console for a few seconds. The student presses the button for at least three seconds.  The instructor asks the student to stop the recording.
